      • compare

        public static int compare​(@NotNull
                          EditorCell firstCell,
                          @NotNull
                          EditorCell secondCell)
        Compares two cells. Cell which is first is the editor is lesser.

        Comparing cells must have common parent. Check getCommonParent(firstCell, secondCell) != null

        Parameters:
        firstCell - a first cell to be compared.
        secondCell - a second cell to be compared.
        Returns:
        -1, zero, or 1 as the first cell is less than, equal to, or greater than the second cell.
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if the first cell and the second cell don't have common parent.

      • iterateTree

        public static CellTreeIterable iterateTree​(@Nullable
                                           EditorCell root,
                                           @NotNull
                                           EditorCell start,
                                           boolean forward)
        Returns a CellTreeIterable that iterates over the subtree of root, in preorder, starting with start.
        Parameters:
        root - the root of the subtree to iterate, null to iterate the whole tree that start is part of.
        start - the first node to visit
        forward - true to visit children of a cell from first to last, false for the reverse order.
        Returns:
        a new instance of CellTreeIterable
